<left>
Once data is stored in an indexed array
it can be retrieved using its index with
the following command: <bigreen>"${ARRAY[N]}"<clear>

To get all the values in an array use: 
<bigreen>"${ARRAY[*]}"<clear> or <bigreen>"${ARRAY[@]}"<clear>
</left>
